Kathleen C., Lisa H., Patty M., & Pinkee P.

data.description: *VA ASSUMABLE 5.75%* Beautiful like new 4/3.5 POOL home located on a quiet preserve! This home features; wood plank tile flooring throughout, open kitchen with stainless steel appliances, spacious living/dining room combo, triple sliders overlook the refreshing salt water pool, screened enclosure and two sun shelves! Full paver patio, pavers have recently been sealed.  Split bedrooms, separate en suite with full bath (at the front of the house), pocket office, barn door, 2 bedrooms with flex room/office/bonus room (can also be used as 5th bd), full bath/pool bath, Large master with lots of storage space! Half bath located off laundry room, freshly painted inside (crushed Ice), plantation shutters, 3 car-garage, huge driveway, sprinkler system, ceiling fans throughout, mini split (ac/heated) in garage, floors have recently been covered with shark coating, and so much more!
